headline: Slim Jim and Buffalo Wild Wings Launch Bold New Chicken Sticks Inspired by Popular Restaurant Chain Sauces
summary: The meat sticks you crave and the sports bar you love are joining forces to create a bold and delicious new offering. Slim Jim®, America's No. 1 meat stick1 from Conagra Brands, Inc. (NYSE: CAG), has partnered with Buffalo Wild Wings®, the largest sports bar brand in the United States2, to offer two new flavor-packed chicken sticks. The tempting new meat snack – available in Buffalo Style and Hot – delivers tender, juicy flavor in a convenient format that's ready to enjoy anywhere.
